data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the highly sought-after Campus Highlands neighborhood! 3 bd, 2.25 ba home boasts 2450 sq ft of comfort and luxury in a desirable locale. Freshly painted exterior. Hardwood floors lead to newer appliances adorning the kitchen and a tiled fireplace, enhancing functionality and style. You'll find three spacious bedrooms with walk-in closets. The primary suite features its own ensuite bathroom, ensuring a private oasis. Step outside to the tranquil Trex deck patio. Immerse yourself in relaxation in your hot tub.This home combines comfort and luxury, making it a rare find in a coveted neighborhood. Don't miss your chance to make this stunning property your own! All information is to be verified by the buyer.
